FOR ANDROID PIPELINE:

Firstly to mention the Triggers, Like where branches would be mentioned and after the commit on branch, the pipeline will automatically triggered.
Install Dependencies.
Change directory to Android and buld the release.
Upload the build in the artifacts of github.
Download the artifact and install and test the realease.


FOR IOS PIPELINE:

Firstly to mention the Triggers, Like where branches would be mentioned and after the commit on branch, the pipeline will automatically triggered.
Install Dependencies.
check the current xcode path.
Installation of POD.
Build the xcarcheive file.
Build the ipa file from xcarcheive file.
Upload that ipa file into artifacts of github.
Download the artifact and install and test the realease.
